PrecisAuthority for (a) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign an AGREEMENT CONCERNING THE IMPOSITION OF IMPORT RESTRICTIONS ON CERTAIN CATEGORIES OF ARCHAELOGICAL ARTIFACTS AND ETHNOGRAPHIC MATERIAL CULTURE between Canada and the UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, or (b) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing either the Hon. Attachments
precis:
Authority for (a) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to
sign an AGREEMENT CONCERNING THE IMPOSITION OF IMPORT RESTRICTIONS ON
CERTAIN CATEGORIES OF ARCHAELOGICAL ARTIFACTS AND ETHNOGRAPHIC MATERIAL
CULTURE between Canada and the UNITED STATES OF AMERICA, or (b) the
Minister of Foreign Affairs to issue an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing either the Hon. Sheila Copps or Raymond Chrétien, to sign the
said Agreement.
